{"tid":1080432,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀，快撚D執]外絮：EA證實大批裁員350位員工，多以行銷營運部門為主","createTime":"2019-03-27T15:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T16:11:41.000Z","uid":21255,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73091e27be3cfd87c43dddaccb39bb2d287daac7","tid":1080432,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"繼上個月動視暴雪（Activision Blizzard）的裁員消息後，另一家海外遊戲大廠美商藝電（Electronic Arts，EA） 也在今（27）日傳出裁員消息，這家擁有 9,000 位員工的公司，約有 350 位員工將被資遣。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒 Kotaku 掌握訊息，EA 執行長 Andrew Wilson 發布裁員聲明，同樣宣稱這是一項困難的決定，被資遣的單位主要來自於行銷、發行、以及營運單位。同時關閉日本、俄羅斯當地辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n<em>作為一家公司企業，我們今日採取一些重要措施來應對挑戰，為未來的機會作好準備。顯然，當觀察周遭不斷變化的世界時，我們必須隨之改變。我們正進行一項深思熟慮的措施，只求兌現我們更好的承諾，完善我們的組織，並滿足我們玩家的需求。有鑑於此，我們對旗下的行銷、發行、以及營運團隊進行組織改動，我們正逐步減少目前在日本和俄羅斯的業務，同時我們也專注於為這些市場中的玩家提供不一樣的服務方式。除了組織變革，我們還相當注重提高遊戲的服務與品質。創造偉大的遊戲依然是我們所做一切的核心目標，我們積極地想激勵玩家並令其感到讚嘆。</em><br />\n<br />\n這是艱難的一天。我們今天所做的改變將影響我們這家擁有 9,000 人公司中約 350 位員工。這是一項很重要卻又困難的決定，我們並沒有因此掉以輕心。在 EA，我們都是朋友和好同事，我們非常感謝並重視每個人的貢獻，我們正盡力確保照顧每一位員工來幫助他們度過這段時間，尋找下一次機會。這是我們的首要目標。<br />\n－ EA 回應 Kotaku 官方聲明<br />\n<br />\n根據 EA 回覆訊息，他們強調每一位離職員工都將獲得遣散費，而 Andrew Wilson 在信函中還特別提到，他們的目標是成為世界上最棒的遊戲公司。<br />\n<br />\n「我們一直希望成為世界上最棒的遊戲公司，」Wilson 寫道：「但如果我們誠實面對自己，我們壓根還沒辦到。我們對於旗下的遊戲、我們與玩家之間的聯繫，以及我們的事業還有很多事情要做。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">EA 去年遭遇《戰地風雲 5》（Battlefield V）因開發期過久銷量不佳的窘境，2019 年原本冀與厚望的大作《冒險聖歌》則是出師不利，因遊戲上市諸多 BUG 設計導致玩家負評如潮，甚至 BioWare 的總監 Casey Hudson 也在官方部落格表達自己對於遊戲煎熬的上市狀況感到「非常失望」。</span><br />\n<br />\n即便 Respwan 團隊《APEX 英雄》（APEX Legends）無預警上架好評爆棚殺出一片天，面對日益嚴重的外掛議題，仍令 EA 不敢大意。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/38364/ea-lays-off-350-people-in-marketing-publishing-and-more?fbclid=IwAR1h7y-48d1Cdh35m05i1hXFqQJmfhBYrP586hljQwdl5gOYFd20ZPBGk84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F38364%2Fea-lays-off-350-people-in-marketing-publishing-and-more%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1h7y-48d1Cdh35m05i1hXFqQJmfhBYrP586hljQwdl5gOYFd20ZPBGk84&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a82f89b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/38364/ea-lays-off-350-people-in-marketing-publishing-and-more?fbclid=IwAR1h7y-48d1Cdh35m05i1hXFqQJmfhBYrP586hljQwdl5gOYFd20ZPBGk84</a>"},{"pid":"0078ebbb9971e6031a0e18b28772936531dbd4b1","tid":1080432,"uid":21255,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"抵死啦屌你老母快撚D執柒左佢啦垃圾公司"},{"pid":"24bf50efe9487db68aaeff00d337c4d932915423","tid":1080432,"uid":21255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/8d6/89f/8d689fa6d7a469c4bfcd825d87d2136721695cf2_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F8d6%2F89f%2F8d689fa6d7a469c4bfcd825d87d2136721695cf2_n.jpg&h=ace1b944&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f96d4bb0497e5b768ddbd26070e25e8c797a579","tid":1080432,"uid":2002,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"好地地打機搞女權<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"c1e0b098a58843a86d75916473e8a9ccec9ebece","tid":1080432,"uid":195438,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"UBI係有心無力<br />\nEA係有力無心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a09a87b8266daf6ea094b2691a376064a6946a","tid":1080432,"uid":136662,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:41:54.000Z","msg":"EA 去年遭遇《戰地風雲 5》（Battlefield V）因開發期過久銷量不佳的窘境<br />\n<br />\n咁都有得賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想食左膠水都唔係咁射波嫁"},{"pid":"ed9d3cdc559478c44dd165b94ac06b515141de03","tid":1080432,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"快撚啲執！"},{"pid":"09d22e3e3f614d50a3e5851bf06b31432b5f2c56","tid":1080432,"uid":49853,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"而 Andrew Wilson 在信函中還特別提到，他們的目標是成為世界上最棒的遊戲公司。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749ba59d8816f160c3af4a7a15aa791cdad9f76f","tid":1080432,"uid":103355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"抵啦， 宜加直頭賣半隻game+唔更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以free DLC名義當玩家狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637f3aa332a4131cdf460c6c190c372bfe0ce2d8","tid":1080432,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T00:43:34.000Z","msg":"EA仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230962d5a059ce4d7dce8df60f214ea9c2cffec8","tid":1080432,"uid":3179,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"EA 最撚仆街係 收購人地 之後再整臭人地隻game<br />\n好多原本好評既大作 落入佢手就變左臭名遠播<br />\n垃圾到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59500e5db4a9e05924036dfdb9c9313507624a8","tid":1080432,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"230962d5a059ce4d7dce8df60f214ea9c2cffec8","tid":1080432,"uid":3179,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"EA 最撚仆街係 收購人地 之後再整臭人地隻game<br />\n好多原本好評既大作 落入佢手就變左臭名遠播<br />\n垃圾到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"應該係直接結束左成個遊戲開發商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma